00:01:11.870 --> 00:01:14.030
But this time,
it's really special

00:01:14.030 --> 00:01:18.400
when I met the people who are
involved with AIM for Seva.

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:22.110
And I met [? Shrini, ?]
[? Shrini ?] and his entire

00:01:22.110 --> 00:01:23.340
team.

00:01:23.340 --> 00:01:29.630
And I went through
Swami [INAUDIBLE]

00:01:29.630 --> 00:01:32.240
preachings, his speeches.

00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:34.520
And I think the kind of
work that they are doing

00:01:34.520 --> 00:01:35.730
is phenomenal.

00:01:35.730 --> 00:01:38.150
I think [? Shrini ?]
will be explaining later

00:01:38.150 --> 00:01:40.970
about what exactly, in detail.

00:01:40.970 --> 00:01:44.960
But the kind of work that
