00:01:44.960 --> 00:01:51.660
They take children right from a
very, very low economic strata

00:01:51.660 --> 00:01:52.160
in life.

00:01:52.160 --> 00:01:53.868
And they take them
all the way, give them

00:01:53.868 --> 00:01:57.980
education, give them
a residence, I mean,

00:01:57.980 --> 00:01:59.780
make their future actually.

00:01:59.780 --> 00:02:05.990
