00:15:21.670 --> 00:15:24.790
And then of course he wrote
the song around the thing.

00:15:24.790 --> 00:15:26.990
And we have many such instances.

00:15:26.990 --> 00:15:33.460
So this trial is very exciting
because we respect each other

00:15:33.460 --> 00:15:36.300
as individuals,
even after 21 years.

00:15:36.300 --> 00:15:42.070
No egos, I think the ego is the
worst thing for a team to have.

00:15:42.070 --> 00:15:45.100
I think, you all know better.

00:15:45.100 --> 00:15:50.312
For a team to exist, coexist
for a long period of time, ego

00:15:50.312 --> 00:15:52.270
is something that you
just leave in your house.

00:15:52.270 --> 00:15:53.997
