00:16:01.795 --> 00:16:02.920
What you say is also right.

00:16:02.920 --> 00:16:04.810
What she says is also right.

00:16:04.810 --> 00:16:10.810
But I think eventually you
have to come to a consensus

00:16:10.810 --> 00:16:13.840
based on what the
melody is telling you.

00:16:13.840 --> 00:16:16.792
It gives out a feeling.

00:16:16.792 --> 00:16:18.250
It gives out a
feeling in that room

00:16:18.250 --> 00:16:20.080
that, yes, this is the melody.

00:16:20.080 --> 00:16:21.140
And we will go with it.

00:16:21.140 --> 00:16:22.960
And when you respect
that, I think

00:16:22.960 --> 00:16:25.210
then everything falls in place.

00:16:25.210 --> 00:16:29.260
And your music, I think it
will work for your music

00:16:29.260 --> 00:16:30.512
